<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ظ ل ف<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣٢٨١ - ظ ل ف]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ظلَفَ يظلِف، ظَلْفًا، فهو ظالِف، والمفعول مَظْلوف<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• ظلَف الصَّيدَ:</span> أصاب ظِلْفه، أي ظُفْره <span class="c1">"ظلَف الصيَّادُ الظبيَ"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• ظلَف الأثرَ:</span> أخفاه لئلاّ يُتْبَع.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>